From 4877f7ab4692489f21cd4c1e0cece0a18216f981 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cory Salisbury <cory.salisbury@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Apr 2026 06:19:01 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] feat: remove all medical references, add e-commerce
 integrations, enhance Performance Hub
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Remove all medical/healthcare branding (MedicalCFO → SellerCFO)
- Remove Salesforce, HubSpot, athenahealth, Kareo, Open Dental integrations
- Add Xero accounting integration alongside QuickBooks
- Add sales channel integrations: Shopify, Amazon, Etsy, WooCommerce, Walmart, TikTok Shop
- Rewrite dashboard Performance Hub with 18 KPIs across 5 categories
- Add KPI toggle sidebar with localStorage persistence
- Add new pages: P&L Center, Inventory HQ, Channel Analytics, AI Insights
- Fix 404 errors by wiring in all dashboard routes
- Update onboarding wizard for e-commerce sales channels
- Update email templates, settings, admin health checks for e-commerce context

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
